Package edu.uno.ai.planning.ss

Contains objects for representing state space search and state space planners.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StateSpaceNode
    Represents a node in a state space search graph.
    StateSpacePlanner
    A planner which searches the space of states for the solution to a given problem.
    StateSpaceProblem
    A subclass of Problem that propositionalizes all the StateSpaceProblem.steps that could possibly occur in a plan.
    StateSpaceRoot
    A special StateSpaceNode that represents the root of the search space and holds a pointer to the search object and the node search limit.
    StateSpaceSearch
    Represents a search space whose nodes are states and whose edges are steps.
